WHO   — The Ghost in the Crontab — the figure behind it all — the job that woke at 3am, that no one commanded and no one watched; the Strangers of Dark City are just cron with better coats (and there is one hidden on this page)
WHAT  — the figure behind it all — the job that woke at 3am, that no one commanded and no one watched; the Strangers of Dark City are just cron with better coats (and there is one hidden on this page)
